[0.514, "o", "\u001b[1m== my-little-claude setup ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.328, "o", "  System: RAM: 64.0GB | CPU: 18x aarch64 | GPU: Apple M5 Pro | OS: macos 26.4 | Tier: High\r\n\r\n  Available models (27 total):\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  [coding]\r\n    [T] rnj-1:8b                           8B  5GB  Dense coding model on par with SOTA. Optimized for code and STEM.\r\n    [T] devstral-small-2:24b              24B  16GB  Mistral coding agent. Best-in-class tool use and multi-file editing.\r\n    [T] qwen3-coder:30b-a3b            30B (3B active)  20GB  Alibaba coding MoE. 128K context, strong tool calling, efficient.\r\n    [T] minimax-m2.7                    Large  40GB  MiniMax coding and agentic workflows model.\r\n  ! [T] qwen3-coder-next               80B (3B active)  50GB  Next-gen Qwen coder. 256K context, 3B active params.\r\n  ! [T] devstral-2:123b                  123B  80GB  Mistral's largest coding model. Exceptional agentic capabilities.\r\n\r\n  [general]\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:0.8b                     0.8B  1GB  Ultra-light. For very constrained environments.\r\n    [ ] llama3.2:1b                        1B  1GB  Meta's tiny Llama. Chat-only, no tool calling.\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:2b                         2B  2GB  Minimal resources. Basic tool calling, "]
[0.000, "o", "fast responses.\r\n    [ ] llama3.2:3b                        3B  2GB  Meta's small Llama. Fast but limited tool calling support.\r\n    [T] ministral-3:3b                     3B  2GB  Mistral tiny edge model. Minimal footprint with tool calling.\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:4b                         4B  3GB  Fast and lightweight. Tool calling, suitable for 8GB machines.\r\n    [T] ministral-3:8b                     8B  5GB  Mistral small edge model. Tool calling on resource-limited hardware.\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:9b                         9B  6GB  Good quality/speed balance. Tool calling, multimodal.\r\n    [T] ministral-3:14b                   14B  10GB  Mistral edge model. Designed for on-device deployment.\r\n    [T] lfm2:24b                          24B  16GB  Liquid AI hybrid model. Designed for on-device deployment.\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:27b                       27B  18GB  Qwen multimodal. Tool calling, 128K context, strong reasoning.\r\n    [T] olmo-3.1:32b                      32B  22GB  AI2 open model. Fully open weights and trai"]
[0.000, "o", "ning data.\r\n    [T] qwen3.5:35b                       35B  24GB  Qwen large. Great quality/speed balance with tool calling.\r\n    [T] kimi-k2.5                         MoE  40GB  Moonshot multimodal agent. Vision + language + tool use.\r\n    [T] llama3.3:70b                      70B  48GB  Meta's largest Llama. Strong coding and tool calling.\r\n  ! [T] qwen3.5:122b                     122B  80GB  Qwen flagship. Multimodal, strong reasoning, tool calling.\r\n\r\n  [reasoning]\r\n    [T] nemotron-3-nano:4b                 4B  3GB  NVIDIA efficient agent model. Good for on-device agentic tasks.\r\n    [T] glm-4.7-flash:30b                 30B  20GB  Zhipu efficient reasoning. Strong planning, multi-step tool use.\r\n    [T] nemotron-cascade-2:30b         30B (3B active)  20GB  NVIDIA MoE. Strong reasoning and agentic capabilities.\r\n  ! [T] nemotron-3-super:120b          120B (12B active)  80GB  NVIDIA large MoE. Complex multi-agent applications.\r\n  ! [T] glm-5:744b                     744B (40B active)  200GB  Zhipu flagship"]
[0.000, "o", " MoE. Complex systems engineering and long-horizon tasks.\r\n\r\n  T = tool calling supported, ! = may not fit in memory\r\n"]
